Release: 3                                         Germany; Leipzig, 22-09-98

               THIS IS ONLY THE COMPLETE ONLINE HELP FOR THE PACKAGE

This package only includes the screenshots and guides. If you want to get the
macros you have to pay a registration fee because of my half year work of 
programming and translating.

@{fg shine}
