    To get this FW Macro Package you have to fillout the @{"registration form" link "register"}!
*******************************************************************************
@{fg text}
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Here it is: The first release of the ultimate Final Writer Macro Package
                  (the third release of the german version)

                 The package includes the following macros:

                       @{" AmigaGuide-Import  " link "AGImport.guide/Main"} V1.0
                       @{" Arrange Objects    " link "ArrangeObj.guide/Main"} V3.0
                       @{" Compress           " link "Compress.guide/Main"} V3.0
                       @{" Database Import    " link "DBImport.guide/Main"} V1.0
                       @{" FontCode           " link "FontCode.guide/Main"} V3.0
                       @{" FontLook           " link "FontLook.guide/Main"} V4.1
                       @{" Footnote Manager   " link "Footnote.guide/Main"} V1.0
                       @{" Guidelines         " link "Guidelines.guide/Main"} V1.1
                       @{" ImprovedTextBlock  " link "ImprovedTextBlock.guide/Main"} V2.1
                       @{" Layouter           " link "Layouter.guide/Main"} V1.1
                       @{" Multiple Paste     " link "MPaste.guide/Main"} V3.0
                       @{" Object Manager     " link "ObjectManager.guide/Main"} V1.0
                       @{" Preview            " link "Preview.guide/Main"} V1.1
                       @{" References         " link "Reference.guide/Main"} V1.0
                       @{" Search & Replace   " link "SearchNReplace.guide/Main"} V2.1
                       @{" Table Column Width " link "TabColoumn.guide/Main"} V1.0
                       @{" Table font         " link "TabFont.guide/Main"} V1.0
                       @{" Windows            " link "Windows.guide/Main"} V1.1

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
     (based on the German version, this is the first release in English)
      The german version is tested by a lot of german registered users.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@{fg shine}
*******************************************************************************
    To get this FW Macro Package you have to fillout the @{"registration form" link "register"}!
*******************************************************************************
@{fg text}
     * To function perfectly some macros need the following @{"programs" link "Progs"}.

     * All macros provide their own graphical user interface, designed according
       to the £User Interface Style Guide¨.

     * All macros include their own @{"menu bar" link Menu} for quick access to
       the standard functions.

     * All macros offer an @{"online help" link Online} function.

     * Preferences can be saved.
 
     * Windows can be iconified to icons to save place on screen.

     * Error messages are displayed in there own window.
 
   Attention:
     Only FW V5 or above allows you to open the macros inside the FinalWriter
     screen.  

     All macros refer to the currently open document, when they are started.
     This means that if you open another document you should close and restart
     the macro to make sure that the macro works with the correct document.

        @{" Questions and Updates " link Autor}

     £Final Writer¨ (TM) is a trademark of Softwood, Inc.

@endnode

