@node Online "Online-help"

   Every macro comes with a online-help function.
   You can access it at any time using the pull-down menu

                   Menu: ? | Help 

   or using the keyboard 

               (right Amiga-key + H)

   You can even read this main guide in Final Writer. To do so
   please run the macro "Help".

@endnode

@node Menu "The menu-bar"

   Every macro offers its own menu-bar.

   Project: 
      Preferences...   - several macros allow to preset some adjustments 

      Quit             - terminates the current macro

   ?:
      Info             - information about the macro

      Help             - opens the online-help for this macro


@endnode

@node Progs "Programs needed"

   The following programs are included in the package. They are 
   automatically installed by the installation program:

   - C:FlushTRX
   - LIBS:reqtools.library
   - LIBS:rexxreqtools.library
   - LIBS:triton.library
   - LIBS:tritonrexx.library

   In addition you need the following tools in your system:

   - C:Delete
   - C:Copy
   - C:List
   - C:Search
   - C:Sort
   - C:Lha
   - C:Lzx
   - SYS:Utilities/Multiview


@endnode
